{"tid":1559912,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【帶頭減租】數碼港向租戶減一半租 為期半年 660企業受惠","createTime":"2019-09-11T04:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T04:40:28.000Z","uid":68738,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7736cea3653ea7c18a398220c4b6dc33cb2e72de","tid":1559912,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190911/large/1568174901_a0cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190911%2Flarge%2F1568174901_a0cf.jpg&h=3cc8e335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n數碼港帶頭減租<br />\n<br />\n香港數碼港宣佈紓緩措施，以協助數碼港的商業租戶及初創應對經濟前景不明朗所帶來的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n數碼港將由今年10月份起，向所有商業租戶及初創公司（包括數碼港内及位於荃灣的 Smart-Space 共享工作間用戶，以及商場内的零售租戶）提供50%的租金寬減，為期6個月。<br />\n<br />\n數碼港主席林家禮表示，預計約660家企業及初創將受惠於是次租金寬減，希望藉此紓緩他們的經營及財政壓力。<br />\n<br />\n對於規模較大的企業，每份租約可享租金寬減的租用面積以1萬平方呎為上限。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190911/60032703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190911%2F60032703&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRegx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=2d21a235\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190911%2F60032703&h=3560fb3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190911/60032703</a>"},{"pid":"2c50250d8c2cc8744e9881890c0ea4adcb75f26a","tid":1559912,"uid":20283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:20:14.000Z","msg":"915呀 又冇人講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1559911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1559911</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dd33b39f4569a9c65df28230969a14309ae4cd5f","tid":1559912,"uid":9230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:24:27.000Z","msg":"呢個死場咁撚大但免費泊車得嗰2個鐘，想睇套長啲嘅戲都唔過啦<br />\n<br />\n要食嘢無，要買嘢無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b84e588257e015088dfe412c2bdb8d309eba37e","tid":1559912,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:26:29.000Z","msg":"Rich7<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf69a10037efe67bf68cf14bbf72ec89542a961","tid":1559912,"uid":28031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開足咁耐死足咁耐既場又想賴？"},{"pid":"de05b327ffa4db9ebcbfb277f9bab4b291545acd","tid":1559912,"uid":16109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:29:01.000Z","msg":"唔再幫李日日賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a00790c7f8ca6c32108ca046ee94f65dde5932","tid":1559912,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"變相用公帑貼囉屌你老母"},{"pid":"6a6e50c2822acc07635913b6a57dfc4ca97179fb","tid":1559912,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:39:17.000Z","msg":"本身都唔多人行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f1f6c690c54d2c40b05920a16a68a23c2cb71c","tid":1559912,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:40:28.000Z","msg":"多謝保皇狗啦"}]}